Key Match Events: David Miller’s fighting century lifts South Africa to a modest total before Cummins’ men, riding on opener Head’s brisk half-century, complete the job after surviving some anxious moments
Post-Match Reflections: The Australians, never ones to back down from a fight, will take on the Indians in what should be a classic final on Sunday
Miscellaneous Highlights: Australia withstood some painful blows to emerge on top by three wickets
